    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone needing dependable transportation. While the engine and transmission are fully functional and have been regularly serviced, there are several signs of wear consistent with its age. The exterior has a few noticeable scratches and minor dings, and the interior upholstery shows some fading and light staining. Additionally, the suspension feels a bit soft, and you should plan on replacing the tires within the next few thousand miles. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without any major mechanical failures.",
