      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a seamless blend of performance and sophisticated engineering. This unit has undergone a comprehensive professional assessment to ensure its mechanical reliability and aesthetic standard are commensurate with our dealership's reputation. Featuring a refined interior and a robust service history, this vehicle represents a premier choice for the discerning driver seeking both longevity and value. We invite you to inspect this distinguished automobile at your earliest convenience.",
      "price": 36500.0,
