    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my car! I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it\u2019s still in really solid shape and running like a dream. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It\u2019s a super reliable ride that\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend trips. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person\u2014I\u2019d love to help you get behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32000.0,
