    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and benefits from a documented VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure structural rigidity, the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The suspension geometry is tight, featuring upgraded bushings for sharpened turn-in response. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the aerodynamic profile and mechanical vitals remain in robust condition. This is a driver-spec example optimized for performance longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
