      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both mechanical integrity and sophisticated design. This selection offers a refined driving experience, characterized by consistent performance and a well-preserved interior. It represents an outstanding value for the discerning professional seeking a vehicle that balances prestige with proven reliability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
