    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road and start some new adventures with you. It\u2019s a great, honest vehicle that handles beautifully. If you\u2019re looking for something dependable and well-loved, this is the one! Feel free to drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
