    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This high-string engine features individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. To ensure long-term reliability, the VANOS unit has been overhauled and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been professionally reinforced. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from refreshed bushings and an M-Variable Differential Lock that provides exceptional corner-exit traction. While the paint shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the mechanical vitals are excellent, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a smooth-shifting synchromesh. This is a mechanically honest example for the purist who prioritizes performance and structural integrity.",
